{"tid":927602,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"奧巴美揚被熱刺球迷掟蕉","createTime":"2018-12-04T09:22:07.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-05T00:59:20.000Z","uid":54373,"like":20,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"a1fd188fd9bd7237dd1756e4464ea324795d6fc6","tid":927602,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:22:07.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.images.dailystar.co.uk/dynamic/1/photos/681000/936x622/1511681.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.images.dailystar.co.uk%2Fdynamic%2F1%2Fphotos%2F681000%2F936x622%2F1511681.jpg&h=c4821695&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴喺英超北倫敦打吡戰主場以4:2砌低熱刺，奧巴美揚梅開二度，原本應該好開心，但其實佢喺比賽初段射入12碼先開紀錄後，曾經被熱刺球迷掟蕉羞辱呀！<br />\n<br />\n奧巴美揚喺開波10分鐘打破僵局，唔知有心定無意走去熱刺球迷面前慶祝，搞到看台上一片粗口聲，期間有人掟蕉入球場，疑似用種族歧視行為作出反擊，結果呢個球迷即時被警察拘捕，熱刺發言人就話呢種行為難以接受，打算禁止佢再入場。<br />\n<br />\n其實熱刺球迷憎奧巴美揚好正常，因為佢可以話勁過頭，賽後足球網站whoscored話佢今場表現有9.3分，而且佢入廠以來，27次聯賽上陣有20個入球同6次助攻，仲當選過今季英超10月最佳球員，簡直係雲格離隊前留畀兵工廠球迷嘅最寶貴禮物。"},{"pid":"0f1681d0ad3c3cdadbe7c75556daef14bef1f923","tid":927602,"uid":44285,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:22:45.000Z","msg":"我叫你柒頭熱"},{"pid":"397875611f92ff0348f9e695de82b69c2651fb7e","tid":927602,"uid":60527,"like":40,"dislike":0,"score":40,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:24:58.000Z","msg":"雲格離隊前留畀兵工廠球迷嘅最寶貴禮物<br />\n<br />\n咸左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bc6a2912d2d053a9b7dfb2954f68fb7acbb3aa74","tid":927602,"uid":49836,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:25:18.000Z","msg":"你當熱狗精神流？"},{"pid":"5ad7f54e9a2ef2402468683f4da18777567530fb","tid":927602,"uid":30478,"like":15,"dislike":0,"score":15,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-04T09:25:23.000Z","msg":"熱刺都有幾個黑人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" cl